he records of female marathon runners improved at a rate three times greater than men's.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the records\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"female marathon runners\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"a rate\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has led many people to question whether,despite a 10-12%performance gap in all distance sports, womenmay surpass menat endurance sports in the future.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10-12%performance gap\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"all distance sports\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"womenmay\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"menat endurance sports\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, due to inequalities in sport the profile, funding and research related to women's sport is lacking.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"inequalities\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"the profile\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The charity Women in Sport suggest this \\\"reflects a wider bias within society\\\".\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The charity\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider bias\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Out of \\u00a335 million the UK government invested into football the women's game received\\u00a33 millionin the 2022-23 financial year.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999109075758, \"rank\": 8.801073264738697e-07, \"text\": \"UK government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's game received\\u00a33\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022-23 financial year\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in 2012 the UK-based Women's Sport and Fitness Foundation argued that women's sport was \\\"sidelined, underfunded and ignored\\\", with their research also suggesting that women's sport received only 0.5% of all commercial sponsorship.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the UK-based Women's Sport and Fitness Foundation\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"their research\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"only 0.5%\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"all commercial sponsorship\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overten years laterthere remains a substantial funding gap.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Overten years\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"a substantial funding gap\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 2023 report commissioned by a woman's sport and entertainment collective which found that 90% of sponsorshipsstill go to men's sport.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A 2023 report\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman's sport and entertainment collective\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"90%\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsorshipsstill\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"men's sport\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a 2023 study by Women in Sport found this lack of funding has a marked impact on career choices with less than29% of girlsand young women aged 13-24 saying they dream of reaching the top in sport compared to over 50% of boys and young men.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 2023 study\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"this lack\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"a marked impact\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"career choices\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"less than29%\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"girlsand young women\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"over 50%\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"young men\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report showed this can change with increased visibility of women's sport.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The report\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"increased visibility\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The number of girls who said they love sport and take part often rose from 50% in 2020 to 69% after theLionesses' Euro win in 2022.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The number\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"50%\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"69%\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"theLionesses' Euro win\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lack of money within women's sport not only affects athletes directly but also has other implications in terms of research and its application to performance.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lack\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"other implications\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"its application\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Research advancements within sport have been pushing the boundaries of what is possible for the human body.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Research advancements\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"the boundaries\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"the human body\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New records in sport can often be attributed to thesport science advancementsthat help athletes to bolster their physical capabilities, aid recovery and rehabilitation and develop their mental strength.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"New records\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"thesport science\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"advancementsthat\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"their physical capabilities\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"aid recovery\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"rehabilitation\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"their mental strength\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is a major problem, nearly all of this research is focused on men with as little as6% of allsport research using female only participants.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a major problem\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly all\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"this research\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"as little as6%\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"allsport research\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"female only participants\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The majority of stakeholders in positions of power within sport who make decisions arepredominantly mensuch as national governing bodies of sport, with control over where funding goes.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The majority\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"stakeholders\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"positions\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"national governing bodies\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of even greater concern is the fact that research conducted on men is being used toexplain female athletic performancewhen women are biologically, physiologically and psychologically different to men.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even greater concern\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"toexplain female athletic performancewhen women\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, research intoVO\\u2082 maxcapabilities (the maximum rate of oxygen your body can use during exercise) have allowed endurance athletes to reach performance feats previously thought to be impossible.\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"research intoVO\\u2082 maxcapabilities\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"the maximum rate\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3435}, {\"ngram\": \"oxygen\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3445}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3455}, {\"ngram\": \"exercise\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance athletes\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3512}, {\"ngram\": \"performance feats\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However most VO\\u2082 max research is based on men and little is known about sex differences.\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most VO\\u2082 max research\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"sex differences\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Researchers in 2022, reviewing the evidence we do have of VO\\u2082 max differences between men and women, concluded that female athletes are being held back by a lack of scientific understanding of female physiology.\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Researchers\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3678}, {\"ngram\": \"the evidence\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3710}, {\"ngram\": \"VO\\u2082 max differences\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3744}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3766}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"scientific understanding\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3856}, {\"ngram\": \"female physiology\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with additional research and the development of more female specific approaches there is no telling the improvements that could be made to female performance.\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 4042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"additional research\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"more female specific approaches\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3963}, {\"ngram\": \"the improvements\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"female performance\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, the 2022 VO\\u2082 max review pointed to studies showing women have some advantages such as superiorfatigue resistance.\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4066, \"end\": 4073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"VO\\u2082 max\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4055}, {\"ngram\": \"studies\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4099}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"some advantages\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4134}, {\"ngram\": \"superiorfatigue resistance\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Researchers often point to the fact that studies with women have to control for more factors.Scientists have notedhow the fluctuations of hormones at different stages of the menstrual cycle as well as menstruation itself present complications when conducting research.\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Researchers\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4207}, {\"ngram\": \"studies\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4231}, {\"ngram\": \"more factors\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4264}, {\"ngram\": \"Scientists\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4275}, {\"ngram\": \"the fluctuations\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"hormones\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4318}, {\"ngram\": \"different stages\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4338}, {\"ngram\": \"the menstrual cycle\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4361}, {\"ngram\": \"menstruation\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4385}, {\"ngram\": \"present complications\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4414}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, this challenge simply demonstrates how little we understand about female athletes.\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this challenge\", \"from\": 4446, \"to\": 4460}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport as a career becomes even more difficult should female athletes wish to become mothers.\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\